CatDescriptText: Broadside reads: "Homecoming dance! & grand raffle of two beautiful handmade ships, now on display at Crawford Grill No. 1, Thurs. May 24th, 9 p.m. until ?, Ritz Cabaret, Fullerton St., sponsored by Twelve Horsemen."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women, including Cleo Blakney Jones wearing light colored suit second from left, and three men, including Walter Jones in center wearing military uniform, seated in banquette at Crawford Grill with venetian blinds and broadside reading "Home Coming Dance!..."
